	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non vacabat copiosius scribere nunc; ergo literas, quas hic vides, optime frater, mitto; tu has proximo trades nuncio commodo, qui ad me reportet bene involutas et obsignatas.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Adieci his et d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2899">Schenkii</persName> literas; ita enim ex tuis te desiderare intellexi; tuae enim bona mihi fide sunt redditae per viduam d. <persName type="auto_name">Nüscheleri</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex <placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Berna</placeName> in horas expecto literas; nam illuc misit tabellionem amplissimus magistratus.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Superioribus diebus ex <placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Berna</placeName> haec ad me perscripsit d. <persName ref="p8018" cert="high">Hallerus</persName>: "Dux <persName ref="p6789" cert="high">Albanus</persName> in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2529" cert="high">Brabantiam</placeName> mittitur, ut ibi instituat inquisitionem <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispanicam</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Praemisit hic comitem ab <placeName type="auto_name">Horn</placeName>, qui paret ipsi viam; hic intellexit esse supra centena virorum consignatorum millia, qui malint interire quam talem admittere tyrannidem; meminisse debere <persName type="auto_name">Philippum</persName>, quibus conditionibus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l808" cert="high">Belgicum</placeName> in eius venerit potestatem."</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dicitur <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispanus</placeName> omnino bellum moliri contra <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832" cert="high">Galliam</placeName> et sua ipsi auxilia polliceri papam et Sabaudum, cum quo iam diu nescio quid egerunt 5 Pag[ici]; <foreign xml:lang="de">dann sy fast geschäfftig und unrüwig sind.</foreign></s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Gott mache sy und andere unrüwige rüwig!</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="de" type="auto">So ir etwas gruntlichs von dem kreißtag vernämend, lassend michs wüssen.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Ich hör, sy wöllend neißwas fasten ansähen, und kumme der fürst von <placeName ref="l572" cert="high">Wirtemberg</placeName> mitt vil pferden dar.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Man sagt ouch, <persName ref="p18477" cert="high">Ferdinand</persName> sye ouch unrüwig und werbe umb knächt.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quae huiusmodi habueris comperta, fac in tempore sciam.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Es sol ouch ein houptman zuͦ <placeName ref="l257" cert="high">Constantz</placeName> sin, <persName type="citizen_name">Hercules Gall</persName>; der sol befälch vomm <placeName type="auto_name">Saffoyer</placeName> haben uff ein fendli lantzknecht, deren sunst och 3 regiment söllend in kurtzem angenommen werden, <foreign xml:lang="la">si modo verum est, quod quidam iactant etc.</foreign></s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Optime vale cum d. <persName type="auto_name">Matthia</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Saluta d. <persName type="auto_name">Huserum</persName> praetorem et <persName type="auto_name">Gislerum</persName> una cum aliis viris bonis.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Salutant te nostri.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ianuarii 23., 1562.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Bullingerus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Ambrosio Blaurero</persName>, domino et fratri suo colendissimo et charissimo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Wintherdur.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
